text: Otylia Tabacka-Kałuża was a middle-distance runner from Poland. Tabacka-Kałuża competed at the 1928 Summer Olympics. She was born on 23 May 1907 and died on 23 October 1981.Otylia Tabacka == References == Category:1907 births Category:1981 deaths Category:Polish middle-distance runners Category:Olympians for Poland
